  <?dbhtml filename="xclock.html"?>

  <title>xclock-&xclock-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The xclock package contains a simple clock application which is used in
      the default xinit configuration.
    </para>

    &not-katamari;

